                <h1>Discover the Joy of Shiba Inu: A Playful Companion</h1>
                <p>Shiba Inu is a charming and spirited dog breed known for its fox-like appearance and lively personality. Originating from Japan, these pups are intelligent, loyal, and often display a playful demeanor. Their iconic curly tails and expressive faces make them a beloved choice among dog lovers. With proper care and training, Shiba Inus can be wonderful companions.</p>
